Project Outcome

The Brazilian E-Commerce Analytics Dashboard successfully transformed raw transactional data into an interactive executive reporting solution. By consolidating multiple datasets into a unified dashboard, the project enabled comprehensive monitoring of sales, customer behavior, logistics, and regional performance. The insights generated help stakeholders identify revenue drivers, operational strengths, and customer retention opportunities, making the dashboard a practical tool for data-driven business decision-making.
